- You usually want the chef
on the beach.

18:12.500 --> 18:14.367
- I'm gonna leave
that up to you.

18:14.367 --> 18:17.100
- Sounds good.
- I know we've got green crew,

18:17.100 --> 18:18.300
but charter guests
don't really give a sh--

18:18.300 --> 18:20.166
how green we are.

18:20.166 --> 18:21.767
- We don't want them knowing
that either, you know?

18:21.767 --> 18:23.367
- As the captain,
you're not allowed

18:23.367 --> 18:25.233
to show your anxiety
to the crew,

18:25.233 --> 18:28.033
but right now the pucker
effect is so strong

18:28.033 --> 18:29.500
you couldn't drive
a straight pin up

18:29.500 --> 18:31.300
my ass with
a 10-pound sledgehammer.

18:31.300 --> 18:32.567
That's a wrap.

18:36.500 --> 18:40.066
- All deck crew, can you go
to the main deck aft please?

