in Portuguese?

19:34.567 --> 19:37.367
- Bon appetit.
- Bon appetit.

19:37.367 --> 19:39.100
- Here we go.
- Do you want to bring it up?

19:39.100 --> 19:40.300
- I think we should.
- Okay, yeah.

19:40.300 --> 19:42.166
