19:42.166 --> 19:44.500
and maybe you would be
interested

19:44.500 --> 19:47.266
in switching rooms,
just one of you.

19:47.266 --> 19:49.667
- So we would have mixed rooms?
- Mm-hmm.

19:49.667 --> 19:52.367
- Is that allowed?
- Yeah, you guys will be fine.

19:52.367 --> 19:56.300
- Later. We were great friends
